# EnrollmentFactsObserved v1 — V2 race-fix (10c8e0bf debrief, 2026-04-26).
# Carries the registry-derived enrollment facts read by EnrollmentRegistryDetector
# (CloudAssignedDomainJoinMethod + CloudAssignedDeviceRegistration / CloudAssignedEspEnabled).
# Reducer handler HandleEnrollmentFactsObservedV1 is stage-agnostic: it does NOT
